---
title: "US56 — Manage user accounts / roles / access"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as System Administrator
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>UsersScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>SetUserStatus
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>User
  A->>B: open Users tab, filter list
  B->>C: listUsers(filter)
  C->>E: listUsers(filter)
  E-->>C: List of User
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (users)
  A->>B: tap Suspend / Activate on a user
  B->>C: setStatus(userId, status)
  C->>E: updateUserStatus(userId, status)
  E-->>C: User (updated status)
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (updated)
  B-->>A: user suspended / activated
  note over E: listUsers / updateUserStatus via SupabaseGateway → profiles (RLS admin-only)
